{"tid":1097022,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]係時候應該新增女性粗口字","createTime":"2019-04-08T06:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T17:22:10.000Z","uid":61861,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f69ed251d5ab9cb434616a46e3dfb305c011c672","tid":1097022,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"既然香港已經男女平等，廣東話應該與時並進，消除父權嘅影響。<br />\n<br />\n廣東話粗口用法千變萬化，但係廣東粗口五大字屌尻閪撚柒有三個半字都男性性器官。<br />\n<br />\n新增粗口字之後就可以衝出嚟柒-&gt;衝出黎嚟__；咪撚再戇尻尻-&gt;咪__再戇__ __，或其他任何用法。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，我係未諗到唔新增字點寫同點讀同點解。<br />\n<br />\n屌：性交、亦指陰莖<br />\n尻：大而硬嘅陰莖，不應硬而硬<br />\n閪：泛指女性的「陰戶、陰部或陰唇」<br />\n撚：陰莖<br />\n柒：大而軟嘅陰莖，大而不當，不靈活者為笨柒<br />\n<br />\n歡迎指正<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.fandom.com/wiki/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%B2%97%E5%8F%A3%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%25B2%2597%25E5%258F%25A3%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%2597&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=70b10344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.fandom.com/wiki/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%B2%97%E5%8F%A3%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%97</a><br />\n《不文集》-黃霑<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇文學底，冇研究過語文"},{"pid":"34aebfe1700c6165d04af61fe8c204755ec0a19c","tid":1097022,"uid":900,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:24:49.000Z","msg":"含你個撚=屌你個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2386ed034a3aa09b1e08670f71d1eaa154c1f7","tid":1097022,"uid":12185,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"已經有啦<br />\n你阿媽個波罩你都冇聽過？<br />\n成句體現出母愛偉大"},{"pid":"3584326a7d9e60147a58387af4a5452c9abc600b","tid":1097022,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b2386ed034a3aa09b1e08670f71d1eaa154c1f7","tid":1097022,"uid":12185,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"已經